            <p>If after your visit you are interested in enrolling your child you must submit an application for enrollment and enrollment deposit to secure  spot in our program or hold a space on our waitlist. If your child is placed on the waitlist your deposit will be held until a space becomes available. If you withdraw your child from the waitlist before a space becomes available, then your tuition deposit maybe refunded, however you must notif the Center in writing. Once a space becomes available and has been reserved for your child you wil not be entitled to a refund. After the application and deposit is received, you will be provided with a welcome packet and asked to schedule your orientation.</p>
            <p>Enrollment at Readway is on a first come, first serve basis and spaces may not be held without an Application for enrollment and Enrollment Deposit. Once our program is full, children will be placed on a waitlist and then be accepted as space becomes available</p>
